            We strive to provide accurate, up-to-date, and complete information on the Site. However, we make no representations or warranties, express or implied, regarding the accuracy, completeness, reliability, suitability, or availability of any information, products, services, or related content on the Site.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Specifically:
          </p>
          <ul class="ml-4 list-disc text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Pricing information</strong> may change without notice. Always verify current pricing directly with the service provider before making a purchase or sign-up decision.</li>
            <li><strong>Company details</strong> (services offered, features, policies, BBB ratings) may change at any time. We review our listings quarterly but cannot guarantee real-time accuracy.</li>
            <li><strong>Third-party ratings</strong> (such as BBB ratings) are provided by those organizations and may be updated at any time without our knowledge.</li>
            <li><strong>User reviews and testimonials</strong> referenced in our content represent individual experiences and do not guarantee similar results.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            You acknowledge that any reliance on information provided on the Site is at your own risk.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. Geographic Restrictions -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mb-4">5. Geographic Restrictions and Service Availability</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            CreditDoc is intended for use by residents of the United States. Some products, services, and advertisements displayed on the Site may not be available in all U.S. states due to state-specific licensing, regulatory, or legal requirements.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We use IP-based geolocation to detect your approximate geographic location and may suppress or modify certain content (including affiliate advertisements and sponsored recommendations) that is not available in your state. This geolocation is approximate and may not always be accurate, particularly if you use a VPN, proxy, or mobile data connection.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            <strong>You are solely responsible for verifying that any financial service provider you engage with is licensed and authorized to operate in your state.</strong> CreditDoc does not guarantee that all services advertised on the Site are available or legally permissible in your jurisdiction. For more information about which services may be restricted in your state, see our <a href="/disclosure/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 6. Third-Party Links -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mb-4">6. Third-Party Links and Websites</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
