            <li>Attempting to gain unauthorized access to the Site or its servers</li>
            <li>Transmitting viruses, malware, or other harmful code</li>
            <li>Engaging in any activity that interferes with other users' ability to use the Site</li>
            <li>Using the Site to harass, threaten, or defame any person or entity</li>
            <li>Scraping, harvesting, or otherwise collecting information from the Site through automated means without our consent</li>
            <li>Impersonating any person or entity or misrepresenting your affiliation with any person or entity</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 9. Disclaimer of Warranties -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mb-4">9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3 uppercase font-semibold">
            THE SITE AND ALL CONTENT, INFORMATION, PRODUCTS, AND SERVICES PROVIDED ON THE SITE ARE PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS WITHOUT ANY WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">
            TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, COSMIC PHOENIX LLC DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO:
          </p>
          <ul class="ml-4 list-disc text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed space-y-1">
