        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to modify, amend, or update these Terms at any time in our sole discretion. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the Site. The "Last Updated" date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision. Your continued use of the Site after any changes to these Terms constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms.
